    "description": "当 SWAT 接到电话时，就意味着其他人员已经失败了。在这个遍布精英 SWAT 操作员的高风险世界里尽情体验吧。 <br> <br> 这份工作很紧张，每个瞬息间的决定都会带来不同的后果。从渗透到降级：敏锐的意识、专业的战术和对设备的战略使用，将为你、罪犯和被卷入中间的任何无辜者带来生与死的差别。<br> <br> 但如果你能保持冷静，你就能成功。每个场景都有其独特的障碍、挑战和致命遭遇。善用各种设备，即使在最严峻的情况下也可以渗透和化解。解锁一系列武器和小工具之后，总能拿出一个不致命的解决方案，虽然这并不容易。<br> <br> 人物角色各有其代表标志，这些标志拥有独特的抽象艺术风格，其颜色和图标可让玩家快速识别出他们所持有的物品和行为。红色表示敌意，黄色表示中立，绿色表示顺从。<br> <br> 与最多四名本地或在线合作玩家一起，不断调整战术并从错误中吸取教训。记住：慢才能顺，顺才能快。<br> <br> 现在让我们看看你的特殊武器和战术吧！<br><br>掌握每项任务：借助各种要解决的地图和场景，每项任务都有一系列的挑战需要学习和克服。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/f2b338cb05d46840b1136f9729b2246b.poster.avif?t=1761641133\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/f2b338cb05d46840b1136f9729b2246b.webm?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/f2b338cb05d46840b1136f9729b2246b.mp4?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每次遇到的设备：你需要利用一切手段渗透并解决每一种情况。为正确的任务找到合适的工具，把每个人安全地带回家。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/d8c9bc34313a3a0c4e87c46788e0f154.poster.avif?t=1761641133\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/d8c9bc34313a3a0c4e87c46788e0f154.webm?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/d8c9bc34313a3a0c4e87c46788e0f154.mp4?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>多个入口点：明显的入口并不总是最适合的。从后面偷袭，把敌人引诱出来，或者干脆炸开墙壁。环境里几乎所有东西都可以破坏，允许玩家破坏窗户、门和墙壁来占据优势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/4ac370dbd1c502642c7ab1a822f6941e.poster.avif?t=1761641133\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/4ac370dbd1c502642c7ab1a822f6941e.webm?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/4ac370dbd1c502642c7ab1a822f6941e.mp4?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>利用周遭环境：无论在什么情况下，都要蹲伏在掩体后面，并滑过低矮的物体，确保自身处于最安全、最有利的位置。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/2cf1965e51c9220d5bff2bbe3e8dc53c.poster.avif?t=1761641133\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/2cf1965e51c9220d5bff2bbe3e8dc53c.webm?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/2cf1965e51c9220d5bff2bbe3e8dc53c.mp4?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>召集伙伴：你可以和 1-4 名玩家在线或本地合作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/4af168d3a5348973537cdf5ba4c0279f.poster.avif?t=1761641133\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/4af168d3a5348973537cdf5ba4c0279f.webm?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/4af168d3a5348973537cdf5ba4c0279f.mp4?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>挑战自我：你能多快把情况都搞清楚？找到最佳策略，逮捕每个犯罪嫌疑人，并让每个人（包括自己的团队）活下来。完美任务的达成条件是零违规零伤亡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/bdbab2e6a0d829ab19f942d9fd6de1ca.poster.avif?t=1761641133\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/bdbab2e6a0d829ab19f942d9fd6de1ca.webm?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892860/extras/bdbab2e6a0d829ab19f942d9fd6de1ca.mp4?t=1761641133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
